Ken yecrek taxxamt-nni akked dadda-s.
Kennemti ɣezzifit anect n baba-twent.
Kennemti ur tettemlelluyemt ara
Kenwi ula d tili-nwen tettaggadem-tt.
Keṛheɣ s kra n wayen yeqqnen ɣer-sen.
Ketbeɣ-as tibṛatin n tayri s tmaziɣt.
Kewweṛeɣ-d yiwet n taɣect d asdegdeg!
Kkes akebbuḍ-ik tferrɣeḍ-d leǧyub-ik!
